title: This Month's GTA+ Benefits
headline: This Month's GTA+ Benefits
content:
In addition to the recurring monthly GTA$500,000 deposited directly into your Maze Bank account, GTA+ members who've signed up for this month (November 9 - December 11) will also receive:

— The Ocelot Pariah
— The Warehouse – Davis property
— Exclusive clothing
— 50% off Super Yacht and Casino Penthouse Modifications
— 40% off Arcade Upgrades and Modifications
— And more

Membership automatically renews monthly, cancel any time. Visit rsg.ms/gtaplus for more info.
